title: Chicken Salad Lettuce Wraps with Grapes and Pecans
directions: In a large bowl, mix together Greek yogurt, lemon zest and juice, mustard, and dill. Season with salt and pepper. Stir in chicken, grapes, pecans, and green onions and season with salt and pepper.
Spoon chicken salad into lettuce leaves, garnish with dill, and serve.
ingredients: 2 tbsp. chopped dill, plus more for garnish
1 rotisserie chicken, skin removed and shredded (3 cups)
4 scallions, white and green parts only, sliced (1/4 cup)
1 head Boston Bibb lettuce, leaves removed
